Package: BNPmix
Type: Package
Title: Algorithms for Pitman-Yor process mixtures
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2018-06-06
Author: Riccardo Corradin
Maintainer: Riccardo Corradin <riccardo.corradin@gmail.com>
Description: A package containing different algorithms to both univariate and multivariate Pitman-Yor mixture models. Estimation could be done via importance conditional sampler, slice sampler or marginal sampler. The package contains also the procedures to estimate via importance conditional sampler a Griffiths-Milne Dependent Dirichlet process mixture model.
License: LGPL-3 | file LICENSE
NeedsCompilation: yes
Imports: methods, ggplot2
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
LinkingTo: RcppArmadillo, Rcpp(>= 0.12.13)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
